endant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"4487741468","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/4487741468","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvNDQ4Nzc0MTQ2OA==","status":"current","title":"Migrar Cardinal 3DS a Cybersource 3DS","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":156},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4487741468/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4487741468","tinyui":"/x/HIB9CwE","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4487741468","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4487741468/Migrar+Cardinal+3DS+a+Cybersource+3DS","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4487741468"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:local-id=\"63e8c255-0bb3-47c9-a87c-9d1a04c3ce24\" ac:macro-id=\"169e060a-632d-4ef5-ad87-d9983fb5bd27\"><ac:rich-text-body><p local-id=\"e9f27c1d-b459-4825-86ad-c16bb6ed4a17\">Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para el proyecto de migraci&oacute;n del flujo 3DS Cardinal a Cybersource en Tpago, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:9e4c7b07-03d5-4a81-a522-cc90518f3086\" ri:local-id=\"480544c5-e72e-42ef-98c5-0d86758b3b2d\" /></ac:link> y <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" ri:local-id=\"e9768c37-cf8c-43fc-8e22-db829ba2655a\" /></ac:link> </p><p local-id=\"fddc80f4-559a-4c30-918f-0efdeb223d55\">Las horas estimadas son: </p><p local-id=\"47cf096a-4206-4384-a06a-7f9f76f074ed\">Fecha de Inicio: a definir</p><p local-id=\"6cdb6630-9cc0-4312-881a-b56c775dca7c\">Fecha de Entrega: a definir</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1 local-id=\"e9b03325-3a02-4635-841e-c873377fa3a3\">Consideraciones Generales</h1><p local-id=\"eb20bc0b-ac09-4191-af45-85b5eee68b13\">El proceso 3DS en cybersource est&aacute; dividido en 5 pasos, los cuales son nuestra gu&iacute;a para el armado de la estimaci&oacute;n:</p><ol start=\"1\" local-id=\"033413ae-9a57-488b-9e7d-fd86fb948610\"><li local-id=\"dddc29a6-a03c-42f5-ac85-4e153cdbd78d\"><p local-id=\"0929a680-cdb1-4638-8bd1-56b0300fd079\"><strong>Setup Service:</strong> llamado a la API de cybersource enviando datos de la tarjeta para obtener la URL y el JWT para el DDC. </p></li><li local-id=\"0cf34911-d84d-4052-9ba4-efecd5a13a5f\"><p local-id=\"1eb762b7-5a25-47ca-beaf-b71b4151a65b\"><strong>Device Data Collection:</strong> llamado a la DDC URL, recolecci&oacute;n de los datos del navegador en iframe invisible.</p></li><li local-id=\"9821f0bb-1861-4df3-9201-a5a7ff32f1a5\"><p local-id=\"de45a5bb-eb41-40b3-b1d9-c18dca2d72b3\"><strong>Payer Authentication Check Enrollment Service: </strong>(ex lookup) llamado a la API de cybersource para conocer el nivel de riesgo de la operaci&oacute;n:<br />- Frictionless success (riesgo bajo)<br />- Challenge required (riesgo moderado)<br />- Frictionless failure or decline (riesgo alto)</p></li><li local-id=\"74dac5dd-8a2b-4bd6-bbd9-35eb126081da\"><p local-id=\"c9d94509-7baa-4943-b16b-875bd83d1a2b\"><strong>Step-Up iframe: </strong>iframe visible donde el usuario completa el challenge para validar su identidad.</p></li><li local-id=\"48c44d1a-1f54-4682-a757-e317ab711d9a\"><p local-id=\"9b0dc9cc-9938-46bb-a8c8-86b69d7bd894\"><strong>Payer Authentication Validation Service: </strong>verificaci&oacute;n de que el usuario valid&oacute; exitosamente su identidad (solo si ocurri&oacute; un challenge). </p></li></ol><h1 local-id=\"c4feb197-69de-4b93-94ea-08aff432a517\">Tpago</h1><p local-id=\"6886a62b-53b7-4c74-acbd-a58adc821e21\">El flujo 3DS en Tpago est&aacute; presente en los flujos:</p><ul local-id=\"08259163-eeb2-4c90-b1b8-4f2d1a511ac1\"><li local-id=\"1fb3a074-b969-4379-bc14-d04ac0b8c945\"><p local-id=\"afa4419f-4535-4271-bde5-4db856139af5\">Pago Ocasional Sin Login (en conjunto con Kount. Si kount est&aacute; activo, solo si kount aprueba. Si kount est&aacute; inactivo, se realiza 3DS)</p></li><li local-id=\"bd6ed197-4f0c-4bc9-ace6-51fd7499856a\"><p local-id=\"c9afd85d-d5df-4ce6-8bdd-8f1f8cd835d4\">Pago Ocasional con Login (Formulario de tarjeta)</p></li><li local-id=\"de29d6a4-8f15-4ab9-9fd0-fade95af88c9\"><p local-id=\"da5b3b99-3cfe-4dfc-a09f-d8b574c1aaba\">Pago con tarjeta catastrada</p></li><li local-id=\"0069f814-89b6-4498-824b-1de5b27bac82\"><p local-id=\"24ea4ddc-5574-4ce8-987a-e436f0ae8b56\">Flujo stripe (Configurable, apagado al momento de escribir este doc)</p></li><li local-id=\"0861f3a6-6ea2-4989-b5fb-bb51a727aeb3\"><p local-id=\"200f7070-7a38-4d47-bf49-f92711c3e41e\">Catastro de tarjetas</p></li></ul><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"5025ca1f-f6c1-4b17-acb7-dfc2ad692d9f\"><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"0a62e8e8-b060-4d91-966e-30ccc0f06365\"><th ac:local-id=\"a9d6acf4-f46c-4cff-8a79-bce736e5d379\"><p local-id=\"1c9f389d-1d2c-4136-a3a3-30eb7f983564\"><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"944012bb-5f09-4042-886c-1a1c5075cd29\"><p local-id=\"3a9e4019-a63d-4a30-a91f-205bb0801b19\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"b53f4c00-67fe-4759-b5b1-c04ea6f7646e\"><td ac:local-id=\"a6c8f634-3f6c-4caf-96fa-8165c3bfdaa3\"><p local-id=\"515aadec-b293-44b5-89b5-5d7023afc025\"><strong>[PASO 1] Setup Service</strong><br />Invocar al servicio de setups para obtener JWT y URL para el DDC. Implementar usando gema oficial <a href=\"https://github.com/CyberSource/cybersource-rest-client-ruby\">cybersource-rest-client-ruby</a> reempazando external-services. Actualizar vistas de pago ocasional y tarjeta catastrada, catastro y stripe.</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"d37e8018-53ce-4230-bb6f-40090286f169\"><p local-id=\"91d3d585-5d3f-4ad3-9450-cc219d9a4dee\">40</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"b14466d1-9794-4dbe-8b7c-540e9eb5f34e\"><td ac:local-id=\"31a277f0-d82f-4a56-a718-7bd86b045768\"><p local-id=\"f45a7557-9fb1-4df1-8c82-bc08e22e1736\"><strong>[PASO 2] Device Data Collection</strong><br />Implementar el iframe y form ocultos para DDC. Capturar el mensaje desde el iframe oculto para habilitar el paso 3.</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"2d95dd22-1db7-4860-94a0-836e354b8dd7\"><p local-id=\"dfff4001-2085-4d7a-8a13-976492bdee30\">40</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"c091a596-2731-4b8f-b35d-2ab025b5bd17\"><td ac:local-id=\"c4dcc6b2-29a7-4080-9f2f-9a612bba688b\"><p local-id=\"179e3324-643c-4537-802e-696da49931fc\"><strong>[PASO 3] Payer Authentication Check Enrollment Service</strong><br />Invocar al servicio usando el <code>referenceId</code> del paso 1. Procesar los posibles resultados (frictionless, challenge, reject). <br />Pendiente: Adaptar l&oacute;gica para NO llamar a JPOS si la respuesta es reject?</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"66600956-53c3-44f8-820f-dcef4c038881\"><p local-id=\"23135559-5232-4ef9-9cc9-159986a19901\">32</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"63568159-01ea-40bb-963f-0f329da15441\"><td ac:local-id=\"0a5aad7d-dba6-4b6d-9cbf-021af02fd949\"><p local-id=\"52710290-9ae2-4791-8e48-027b922f42a0\"><strong>[PASO 4] Step-Up iframe</strong><br />Implementar el iframe visible para el challenge. Integrar el <code>stepUpUrl</code> y <code>accessToken</code> recibidos en el punto 3. Gestionar el callback: eliminar websockets y reemplazar por mensajes de javascript.</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"aee12b5b-5609-45f7-bc3f-632d9bdef2e2\"><p local-id=\"358562b5-679b-44e9-a38c-0ce60fdff2d5\">56</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"d0659a2b-9f1f-4448-9388-f3299f8f7066\"><td ac:local-id=\"4363dcb0-17f5-4ec5-8051-480017563958\"><p local-id=\"4b909416-8574-4d84-8cd8-43d453eaa057\"><strong>[PASO 5] Payer Authentication Validation</strong> Verificar el resultado del challenge (si ocurri&oacute;). Invocar el endpoint de validaci&oacute;n y procesar la respuesta antes de autorizar el pago.</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"47027312-f89f-497a-b5f9-ba15646375fb\"><p local-id=\"2a423479-6e54-4c3e-a59b-902f621e2469\">24</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"57153af6-5ce1-4df2-8d78-1bcb23938b19\"><td ac:local-id=\"3d592d0c-e672-454a-b018-a3afdb72ac0e\"><p local-id=\"9b3b2bfc-4150-4727-b00d-bc6c907ada06\"><strong>Integraci&oacute;n y pruebas en Staging</strong>\n- Integraci&oacute;n de los flujos\n- Creaci&oacute;n y correcci&oacute;n de PRs\n- Pruebas locales\n- Armado de ramas\n- Deploy a STG\n- Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"643567da-65b6-44e5-b66b-bc29f50dbeee\"><p local-id=\"1c734d5d-1bb8-4fb7-99f9-ae1bc03fd7aa\">24</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"0e8665ba-531b-47f2-b977-b358a54d052a\"><td ac:local-id=\"b9ae2d69-1463-49a8-997d-c9f8e34dcf81\"><p local-id=\"15944d93-3b7a-4d6a-a827-ea3ba1c739c1\"><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"95722205-506d-4119-8949-9011b8e8f24b\"><p local-id=\"124886e8-78dd-4fb4-9f4c-f70f0980cafd\">216</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"acb3a33a-1899-471c-b764-b4859b866fdb\"><td ac:local-id=\"fd96e57b-5a81-4f7c-97e2-930b586c35e4\"><p local-id=\"c4aebd4b-1141-4fb2-aaeb-96cd6f71583f\"><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15%</strong>\nIncluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"a93a27d2-8607-470b-b539-ecc1517d2c96\"><p local-id=\"087269f1-8e6f-4617-b2a4-5a6c02564d6d\">32</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"9ac5c06b-b37e-464b-a184-4767e7a0036a\"><td ac:local-id=\"8ca36b35-95ab-42d3-8f54-b84141a6712d\"><p local-id=\"1c5ca788-f7ae-4727-a0eb-f38962121d6e\"><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td ac:local-id=\"2b9a23e9-91ba-4c03-b76a-2d888f0dfebb\"><p local-id=\"ea099ca0-1947-41f7-8abc-7a19a5f281ab\">248</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4812734465"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":3351},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4812734465/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4812734465/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4812734465/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4812734465/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4812734465","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4812734465/Tpago+-+3DS+Cybersource+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4812734465","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4812734465","tinyui":"/x/AYDcHgE","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}